{"tid":1912891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓反擊封關 下周一起暫停日本公民免簽證入境","createTime":"2020-03-06T11:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T13:22:08.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"333be950f770fb693e1bd9e4f501be038b679124","tid":1912891,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"日本要求下星期一起，訪日的南韓旅客隔離14日，並取消免簽證入境安排。措施演變成外交鬥爭，引發南韓反日情緒，南韓政府宣布取消日本人免簽證入境安排。<br />\n<br />\n青瓦台召開國家安全保障會議後亦表示極度遺憾，又對日本事前未有充分與韓方溝通感到費解，並藉機批評日本採取不透明且消極的防疫措施，不獲國際社會信任。"},{"pid":"93224cea071902ce509603869c9ab2581a0dc444","tid":1912891,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T11:36:18.000Z","msg":"南韓外長康京和罕有親自召見日本駐韓大使富田浩司提出抗議，康京和批評日本的措施不友善亦無科學根據，促請日本盡快撤回，不然南韓會研究在對等原則下採取措施回應。<br />\n<br />\n日本外相茂木敏充回應說，加強入境管制是為了防止日本國內疫情蔓延，南韓感染人數正激增是事實。"},{"pid":"c212e104a50905966750bac4b7c0e132456d22b3","tid":1912891,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T11:38:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383258&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=8b3fe59b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D383258&h=51f69a39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=383258</a>"},{"pid":"990953d812686bd09114c5d0d56041296a29520f","tid":1912891,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b8f5a770000bcbec2f49c67cebf9f94523dd39","tid":1912891,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e5343e5610046423579c82c4d